title: Rose Letter V Monogram Initial Pink Flowers Black
features: This beautiful letter V monogram phone grip for phones features a fancy lettered first initial on a black graphic and is adorned with pretty pink flowers in the design.

Advanced adhesive allows you to remove and reposition on most devices and cases.
